449
00:25:23,270 --> 00:25:25,860
Are you giving me a chance
to mark my territory

450
00:25:25,990 --> 00:25:27,860
in your new house?

451
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,110
Before,

452
00:25:39,030 --> 00:25:40,470
I never thought

453
00:25:40,470 --> 00:25:42,710
about letting others into my life,

454
00:25:42,860 --> 00:25:44,670
but this time,

455
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:47,510
I want to give it a try.

456
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:50,260
