496
00:28:45,300 --> 00:28:46,140
What's wrong?

497
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:49,140
I'll talk to him tomorrow.

498
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:49,990
No need.

499
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:52,060
He's busy.
What don't you tell me instead?

500
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:56,540
