502
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:01,620
I'll talk to Fang about it later.

503
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:03,230
You're not very good with these things.

504
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:04,670
He's been working overtime lately.

505
00:29:04,670 --> 00:29:05,820
You can't catch him.

506
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:07,750
No rush, no rush.

507
00:29:08,910 --> 00:29:11,300
