522
00:30:16,620 --> 00:30:17,780
When I got back, I looked him up.

523
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:19,820
His works

524
00:30:21,470 --> 00:30:22,430
match this color scheme.

525
00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:25,140
You painted this wall?

526
00:30:26,540 --> 00:30:27,380
Yes.

527
00:30:33,950 --> 00:30:35,270
You arranged this house?

528
00:30:39,190 --> 00:30:41,060
