530
00:30:44,470 --> 00:30:45,470
That's too hard.

531
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:46,750
I couldn't do that.

532
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:52,750
That day you mentioned so many artists.

533
00:30:53,710 --> 00:30:54,580
Konstantinovich,

534
00:30:55,230 --> 00:30:56,140
Mondrian,

535
00:30:56,820 --> 00:30:57,660
and also

536
00:30:58,510 --> 00:30:59,350
Kubota.

537
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:01,620
I looked them all up.

538
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:03,710
This was the simplest.

539
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:07,190
So you painted the wall like this

540
00:31:07,190 --> 00:31:08,860
