541
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:11,860
This house is originally narrow and dark.

542
00:31:13,140 --> 00:31:14,230
I was afraid you wouldn't like it.

543
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:15,460
What else?

544
00:31:17,860 --> 00:31:18,700
There's more.

545
00:31:19,300 --> 00:31:20,860
I asked your classmates and found out

546
00:31:21,340 --> 00:31:23,140
