a coder's clumsy methods,

561
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:55,990
using algorithms
to find a path close to you.

562
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:58,540
Sometimes, I might use a few

563
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:01,030
small programs, little tricks.

564
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,110
But I believe

565
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:05,340
as long as the destination is right,

566
00:32:06,340 --> 00:32:08,430
the process of the program
doesn't matter.

567
00:32:08,710 --> 00:32:09,710
Good talker.

568
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:11,110
Rose,

569
00:32:11,430 --> 00:32:12,270
